    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《斯科普里83：湮灭前夕》是一款融合轻度肉鸽与开放世界玩法的漫画风第一人称射击游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/5c8d3fd3061c06282a6a957f560667d7.poster.avif?t=1762524557\" width=600 height=285 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/5c8d3fd3061c06282a6a957f560667d7.webm?t=1762524557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/679d42c47ab7cc31ab23183ecb4a754a.avif?t=1762524557\" width=600 height=83 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在求生的同时与时间赛跑！玩家需要限时七天内解除由数个能量塔形成的穹顶，让外界支援进入城内。如果未能完成任务，一场爆炸将摧毁整个城市。而玩家将回到第一天，重新被唤醒，再次开始征程。这种末日循环让游戏充满了变数和挑战。每次死亡或失败，玩家将面临技能重置、物资丢失、敌人重生，你将不得不再次杀出一条血路。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/16f401738bf09f718a28547a420e5cda.poster.avif?t=1762524557\" width=600 height=285 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/16f401738bf09f718a28547a420e5cda.webm?t=1762524557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/2c63a5134e356a1ec464b1ddf500e24e.avif?t=1762524557\" width=600 height=83 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对城中的混乱和疯狂，“末日巴士”是你坚实的移动堡垒。在这里，你能够升级装备、制作武器、储存生存物资、获得技能加成、安心休息恢复体力。同时，你还能升级改造自己的战车：更大的空间、更强的防御、更高的性能。只为在关键时刻突出重围，碾过源源不断的丧尸，更快前往这片开放世界的下一个目的地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/64160d9a4e37d1e4b1c07b8bcb5060bf.poster.avif?t=1762524557\" width=600 height=285 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/64160d9a4e37d1e4b1c07b8bcb5060bf.webm?t=1762524557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/a6a6f0cdee9a07e842c8d5e21f25d6c0.avif?t=1762524557\" width=600 height=83 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《斯科普里83：湮灭前夕》采用独特的漫画风格打造末日中的斯科普里，这个充满视觉冲击力的世界。这座城市融合了复古未来主义设计，在上世纪70-80年代怀旧与硬核科幻之间找到了奇妙的平衡，城市的建筑和载具融入了浓郁的巴尔干风格，让玩家在探索过程中不断感受到时空交错的独特魅力。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/0746591308e92c8fa5746a73ab16c630.poster.avif?t=1762524557\" width=600 height=285 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/0746591308e92c8fa5746a73ab16c630.webm?t=1762524557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/090b67db1782edc9631a087596416c1f.avif?t=1762524557\" width=600 height=83 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《斯科普里83：湮灭前夕》支持多人联机组队，队友将祝你一臂之力。在这座被赛博僵尸占领、危机四伏的都市中，玩家作为被唤醒的先遣者，单枪匹马作战往往困难重重，只有齐心协力，才能在这个残酷的末日世界中更好地生存下来，完成艰巨的任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/ec99b2a80eec7fc0b3a299edccf8d1f8.poster.avif?t=1762524557\" width=600 height=285 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211980/extras/ec99b2a80eec7fc0b3a299edccf8d1f8.webm?t=1762524557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
